{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FederatedCredential","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Credential_Management_API\">Credential Management API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential\"><code>FederatedCredential</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/FederatedCredential\"><code>FederatedCredential()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/protocol\"><code>protocol</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/provider\"><code>provider</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Credential\"><code>Credential</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Credential Management API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Credential\"><code>Credential</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CredentialsContainer\"><code>CredentialsContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PasswordCredential\"><code>PasswordCredential</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PublicKeyCredential\"><code>PublicKeyCredential</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>FederatedCredential</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Credential_Management_API\">Credential Management API</a> のインターフェイスで、連合アイデンティティのプロバイダーからの認証情報についての情報を提供します。連合アイデンティティのプロバイダーは、ウェブサイトが正しくユーザーを認証し、そのための API を提供する主体です。連合アイデンティティプロバイダーの一例として、 <a href=\"https://openid.net/developers/specs/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">OpenID Connect</a> があります。</p>\n\n<p>対応しているブラウザーにおいては、このインターフェイスのインスタンスがグローバル <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/fetch\"><code>fetch</code></a> の <code>init</code> オブジェクトの <code>credential</code> メンバーとして渡されることがあります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"コンストラクター","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"federatedcredential_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/FederatedCredential\"><code>FederatedCredential()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>新しい <code>FederatedCredential</code> オブジェクトを生成します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>祖先である <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Credential\"><code>Credential</code></a> からプロパティを継承しています。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"federatedcredential.provider_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/provider\"><code>FederatedCredential.provider</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>認証情報の連合アイデンティティプロバイダーを含む <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"federatedcredential.protocol\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/protocol\"><code>FederatedCredential.protocol</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>認証情報の連合アイデンティティプロトコルを含む <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> です。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"event_handlers","title":"イベントハンドラー","isH3":true,"content":"<p>なし。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<p>なし。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> cred <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FederatedCredential</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">provider</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://account.google.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">iconURL</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> iconUrl\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 格納</span>\nnavigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>credentials<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">store</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>cred<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 他に何かをする</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webappsec-credential-management/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Credential Management Level 1の仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">Credential Management Level 1</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.FederatedCredential","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"コンストラクター","id":"constructor"},{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"FederatedCredential は Credential Management API のインターフェイスで、連合アイデンティティのプロバイダーからの認証情報についての情報を提供します。連合アイデンティティのプロバイダーは、ウェブサイトが正しくユーザーを認証し、そのための API を提供する主体です。連合アイデンティティプロバイダーの一例として、 OpenID Connect があります。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FederatedCredential","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"FederatedCredential","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FederatedCredential","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/federatedcredential","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/federatedcredential/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential","title":"FederatedCredential"}],"pageTitle":"FederatedCredential - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}